      "Stage: first real traction — the first concrete action inside the first stepping stone. Homework MUST come from the client and MUST be sized so the S9 top restrainer cannot credibly block it. If restrainer = procrastination → action small enough to do the day of or the day after (a 20-minute block, a single email, a single phone call). If restrainer = fear-of-visibility → action should still be private (draft, not publish; outline, not share). If restrainer = perfectionism → action has a hard time-box shorter than the urge to polish (45 minutes, one pass, done). Include a WITNESS: one specific person the client will tell about the action before the week is out — not to hold them accountable in a heavy way, just to speak it out loud. Save witness as person memory if not already.",
